title: Windows Vista x86 Incl SP1 March 2009(No Activation Needed)
description:
Microsoft Windows Vista x86 SP1 OEM DVD Integrated March 2009 (C)2008 Microsoft Corp.

No Serial and no Activation needed

HowTo:
1. Burn .gbi image file with gBurner to DVD at slowest write speed.

2. Boot from disc, select or make a partition and reformat it before installing. Do NOT install this over top of an existing Windows version, as it sometimes won't work correctly

3. Do NOT enter a serial/product key during install

4. Do not set a password for your user-account during setup

5. Do NOT interrupt the install. Don't be in a hurry if it seems to stall. Sometimes a poor quality burn can cause it to hang, but simply waiting could help this
